# Privacy Policy for Pomodoro Clock

**Effective Date:** January 25, 2025  

At **[Your Extension Name]**, your privacy is our top priority. This privacy policy explains how we handle your data when you use our browser extension.

## Data Collection
We do **not** collect, store, or share any personal or sensitive data from users. All functionalities of this extension, such as setting timers and opening new tabs for notifications, are performed locally on your device. No information is transmitted to external servers or third parties.

## Permissions
The permissions requested by this extension (e.g., opening tabs, notifications) are strictly used to deliver its core functionality. These permissions do not involve accessing or transmitting any personal data.

## Changes to This Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted here, so please review it periodically.

## Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, feel free to contact us at **hemasharan3050@gmail.com**.
